    <div id="header">Process Overflow</div>
    <div id="container">
    <p>OUR WORKFLOW</p>
<div class="m1"><br>E-Waste Management is a complex and multi-layered task.<br>We adopt a systematic, clearly outlined process that includes:<br>
<br>
    <div class="y">1.Collection<br></div>
Our team visits your place and collects your e-Waste materials.<br>
<br>
    <div class="y">2.Transportation<br></div>
The materials are loaded into our specialized carriers and brought to our storage and dismantling facility on the outskirts of Pune<br>
    <br>
    <div class="y">3.Segregation<br></div>
Hazardous substances are identified and separated out.<br>
<br>
    <div class="y">4.Dismantling<br></div>
The systems are dismantled into smaller parts/components so as to facilitate recycling.<br>
<br>
    <div class="y">5.Recycling<br></div>
    Actual recycling in an eco-friendly way takes place as per stringent norms laid down by the authorities.<br></div>
    </div>
